      <section eId="sec_2504">
        <num>2504</num>
        <heading>Waiver of undertaking; removal and change of parties</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_2504__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>\nWaiver of undertaking. Unless the court orders otherwise, an undertaking\nmay be waived by the written consent of all parties.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_2504__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Removal and change of parties. The liability on an undertaking\nshall remain in effect in favor of the party for whose benefit it was\ngiven, notwithstanding a removal of the action or a change of parties.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
